https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a62d42bfebcc4d029e30cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225773%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20(not%20pictured)%20says%20her%20almost%2016-year-old%20is%20not%20running%20to%20get%20a%20driver's%20license.%3Cp%3Erecep-bg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20state%20requires%20people%20under%2018%20to%20take%20costly%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fodh.ohio.gov%2Fknow-our-programs%2Fchild-injury-Prevention%2Fteen-driving%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAt%2520age%252015%2520years%2520and%2Cfor%2520at%2520least%2520six%2520months.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edriver's%20education%20classes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20almost%2016-year-old%20is%20waiting%20to%20get%20his%20license%20until%20he's%20older.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe's%20fine%20with%20me%20driving%20him%20around%20and%20doesn't%20want%20to%20learn.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20son%20recently%20became%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-a-drivers-license-us-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eold%20enough%20to%20get%20his%20learner's%20permit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20In%20the%20state%20of%20Ohio%2C%20that's%2015%20years%20and%20six%20months%20of%20age.%20But%20he's%20not%20remotely%20interested%20in%20pursuing%20getting%20his%20driver's%20license.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20considerable%20research%20and%20thought%2C%20I%20support%20his%20decision.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a641f825-8fbe-4052-9ade-82ae5c5c642b%5C%22%3EI%20couldn't%20wait%20to%20get%20my%20license%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-xers-moving-retirement-areas-florida-texas-new-york-cities-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI'm%20Gen%20X%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20when%20I%20was%20in%20high%20school%2C%20most%20teenagers%20couldn't%20wait%20to%20get%20their%20driver's%20licenses%20and%20the%20potential%20for%20independence%20that%20came%20with%20them.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20my%20family%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20get%20me%20a%20car%2C%20the%20potential%20to%20visit%20friends'%20houses%20or%20just%20drive%20around%20by%20myself%20using%20my%20mom's%20car%20was%20a%20huge%20motivator.%20I%20craved%20independence%20as%20a%20teenager%2C%20and%20wanted%20to%20get%20away%20from%20my%20mom%20and%20the%20house%20whenever%20I%20could.%20I%20got%20my%20permit%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20could%20and%20learned%20how%20to%20drive%20through%20inexpensive%20classes%20(about%20%2450)%20through%20a%20local%20driving%20school.%20I%20passed%20my%20test%20on%20the%20first%20try.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20knew%20my%20son%20wasn't%20super%20hot%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-be-a-better-driver-2017-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elearn%20to%20drive%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Like%20many%20of%20his%20Gen%20Z%20peers%2C%20he%20doesn't%20have%20much%20of%20an%20external%20social%20life%20outside%20school%20and%20participation%20in%20marching%20band%2C%20which%20occupies%20the%20latter%20half%20of%20each%20year.%20Outside%20school%2C%20he%20connects%20with%20friends%20through%20online%20games%20or%20video%20calls.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228da6bc6f-131c-4364-a089-21ad50f5c049%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20thought%20he'd%20be%20driving%20by%20now%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-son-is-getting-his-drivers-license-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20thought%20he%20might%20be%20driving%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20work%20by%20this%20age%2C%20at%20least%20to%20a%20summer%20job.%20I%20had%20to%20get%20a%20job%20to%20contribute%20to%20household%20expenses%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20was%20old%20enough%20to%20work%2C%20and%20worked%20after%20school%20and%20on%20weekends%20the%20last%20two%20years%20of%20high%20school.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20between%20marching%20band%2C%20which%20starts%20in%20early%20August%2C%20and%20my%20shared%20custody%20schedule%20with%20his%20dad%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20another%20city%2C%20my%20son%20being%20consistently%20available%20for%20any%20kind%20of%20summer%20job%20has%20been%20impossible%20as%20he%20only%20has%20a%20few%20weeks%20free%20each%20summer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20considerable%20research%2C%20I%20support%20his%20decision%20not%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-was-my-dads-designated-driver-when-he-drank-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eget%20a%20license%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20reasons%20we%20have%20both%20decided%20it's%20best%20for%20him%20to%20wait%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20those%20rare%20occasions%20where%20my%20teen%20and%20I%20are%20on%20the%20same%20page.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22486e78ba-a50b-47ed-9acf-a9a02a9bcae6%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EClasses%20can%20be%20expensive%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20Ohio%20law%20requires%20that%20anyone%20under%2018%20who%20wants%20a%20driver's%20license%20attend%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcountries-cost-price-driver-license-comparison-2018-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaccredited%20driving%20school%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20several%20weeks.%20Few%20of%20these%20schools%20exist%2C%20which%20allows%20them%20to%20monopolize%20the%20market%20and%20make%20the%20classes%20very%20expensive%20(around%20%24700).%20Right%20now%2C%20that's%20a%20big%20financial%20reach%20for%20me.%20He%20must%20also%20have%2050%20hours%20of%20driving%20experience%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20classes%2C%20which%20would%20all%20be%20my%20responsibility.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20said%20he%20prefers%20I%20teach%20him%20when%20he's%20ready%20to%20learn%2C%20but%20like%20most%20teenagers%20and%20parents%2C%20our%20communications%20can%20be%20fraught%20with%20disagreements%20and%20push-back.%20Getting%20him%20to%20listen%20to%20me%20during%20driving%20lessons%20at%20this%20age%20would%20be%20challenging.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecondly%2C%20in%20Ohio%2C%20if%20you%20wait%20until%20you%20are%2018%20to%20get%20your%20license%2C%20you%20can%20skip%20the%20class%20and%20have%20a%20friend%20or%20parent%20teach%20you%20to%20drive.%20But%20if%20you%20fail%20the%20test%20the%20first%20time%20you%20take%20it%2C%20you%20must%20take%20the%20expensive%20classes%20anyway.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20third%20factor%20is%20safety.%20Some%20people%20might%20argue%20that%20it's%20safer%20for%20younger%20drivers%20to%20wait%20to%20get%20their%20licenses%2C%20and%20the%20statistics%20are%20hard%20to%20ignore.%20According%20to%20the%20Insurance%20Institute%20for%20Highway%20Safety%2C%20though%20they%20drive%20fewer%20miles%20than%20older%20people%2C%20drivers%20ages%2016%20to%2019%20are%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iihs.org%2Ftopics%2Fteenagers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efour%20times%20more%20likely%20to%20crash%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20than%20drivers%20over%2020%2C%20and%20these%20crashes%20are%20the%20leading%20cause%20of%20death%20for%20people%20in%20this%20age%20bracket.%20Risk%20is%20highest%20at%20the%20age%20of%2016%2C%20which%20is%20just%20about%20how%20old%20my%20son%20is%20now.%20To%20be%20completely%20honest%2C%20this%20scares%20me%20a%20lot.%20I%20could%20only%20have%20one%20child%2C%20and%20parenting%20him%20has%20been%20the%20best%20thing%20I've%20done.%20The%20thought%20of%20losing%20him%20in%20a%20crash%20is%20terrifying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFinally%2C%20there's%20the%20insurance%20factor.%20Most%20people%20know%20generally%20that%20it's%20quite%20expensive%20to%20add%20a%20teenager%20to%20their%20auto%20insurance%20policy%2C%20but%20teen%20boys%20cost%20more%20to%20insure%20than%20teen%20girls.%20That's%20because%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caranddriver.com%2Fcar-insurance%2Fa36164061%2Faverage-car-insurance-rates-by-age-and-gender%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estatistically%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20boys%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20accidents.%20They're%20also%20more%20likely%20to%20engage%20in%20risky%20behavior%20behind%20the%20wheel%2C%20including%20driving%20after%20drinking%20alcohol.%20I%20called%20my%20insurance%20provider%20to%20inquire%20about%20a%20quote%20and%20was%20told%20that%20adding%20my%20kid%20to%20the%20policy%20as%20a%20driver%20would%20double%20my%20rates.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229cc3ba9b-4528-47b7-9fe8-4d0b1e9fd568%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMaybe%20his%20generation%20is%20onto%20something%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20researching%20all%20of%20this%2C%20I%20began%20to%20reconsider%20whether%20my%20kid%20being%20on%20the%20road%20is%20good%20for%20anyone%20%E2%80%94%20him%2C%20other%20drivers%2C%20or%20me%2C%20considering%20the%20worry%20and%20stress%20I%20would%20have%20every%20time%20he%20gets%20behind%20the%20wheel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMaybe%20Gen%20Z%20is%20smarter%20than%20I%20was%20at%20their%20age.%20Not%20long%20after%20I%20got%20my%20license%2C%20I%20took%20Mom's%20car%20to%20a%20friend's%20house%20to%20make%20signs%20for%20a%20football%20game%20the%20next%20night.%20My%20family%20lived%20in%20poverty%2C%20and%20my%20mom's%20Honda%20Civic%20was%20not%20well-maintained%2C%20including%20bald%20tires%20and%20a%20propensity%20to%20stall%20if%20you%20didn't%20give%20it%20enough%20gas.%20The%20combination%20of%20a%20dangerous%20vehicle%20and%20dark%2C%20rainy%20road%20conditions%20resulted%20in%20me%20crashing%20into%20a%20telephone%20pole%20that%20night%2C%20which%20slammed%20down%20onto%20the%20car%20and%20could%20have%20killed%20me%20and%20my%20passenger.%20Fortunately%2C%20but%20for%20a%20few%20bruises%20and%20me%20with%20two%20black%20eyes%2C%20we%20walked%20away%20unscathed%2C%20though%20the%20car%20was%20totaled.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20son%20has%20also%20figured%20out%20that%20if%20he%20had%20access%20to%20a%20car%2C%20he%20would%20be%20required%20to%20chip%20in%20to%20help%20offset%20the%20costs%2C%20and%20he%20sees%20no%20upside%20to%20that.%20His%20grades%20are%20quite%20good%2C%20but%20his%20honors%20coursework%20is%20very%20challenging%2C%20and%20he%20has%20been%20frank%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20thinks%20school%20is%20enough%20work.%20He%20doesn't%20want%20to%20spend%20his%20free%20time%20working%20every%20spare%20minute.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20pointedly%20said%20my%20driving%20him%20everywhere%20is%20%26quot%3Bgreat%26quot%3B%20for%20him%20and%20asked%20me%20why%20he%20would%20go%20through%20all%20the%20trouble%20(and%20my%20expense)%20of%20driving%20when%20what%20we've%20been%20doing%20works%20for%20him.%20With%20the%20cost%20and%20risk%20involved%20in%20making%20him%20a%20licensed%20and%20insured%20driver%2C%20I%20agree.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes%2C%20it's%20more%20of%20a%20pain%20in%20my%20ass%20to%20drive%20him%20everywhere%2C%20but%20it's%20saving%20me%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20stress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-teenager-is-waiting-to-get-his-drivers-license-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739202361000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a62e5ebfebcc4d029e311f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F