ussian%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIgor%20Potapov%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Russian%20manufacturer%20JSC%20NPP%2C%20told%20state-controlled%20news%20agency%20TASS%20that%20an%20individual%20donated%20the%20goggles%20as%20humanitarian%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20glasses%20were%20turned%20on%2C%20they%20detonated%20and%20exploded%2C%26quot%3B%20Potapov%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETASS%20did%20not%20specify%20whether%20there%20had%20been%20any%20injuries%20or%20fatalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Potapov%2C%20the%20goggles%20were%20Skyzone%20Cobra%20X%20v4%20headsets%2C%20used%20to%20provide%20a%20visual%20when%20controlling%20first-person%20view%20drones.%20He%20added%20that%20when%20the%20military%20opened%20the%20batch%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20found%20plastic%20explosives%20in%20all%20of%20the%20products.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20was%20unable%20to%20independently%20verify%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESkyzone%20supplies%20companies%20in%20multiple%20countries%2C%20including%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%2C%20but%20does%20not%20list%20JSC%20NPP%20among%20its%20distributors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20company%20immediately%20responded%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDefense%20Intelligence%20of%20Ukraine%20has%20not%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20reported%20sabotage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsumer-grade%20FPV%20drones%20are%20used%20in%20their%20thousands%20by%20both%20Ukraine%20and%20Russia%2C%20for%20everything%20from%20surveillance%20and%20reconnaissance%2C%20to%20target%20spotting%20and%20carrying%20explosives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPro-Russian%20Telegram%20channel%20Razved%20Dozor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frazved_dozor%2F7748%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshared%20images%3C%2Fa%3E%20purporting%20to%20be%20of%20the%20headsets%20still%20in%20their%20boxes%2C%20along%20with%20video%20of%20them%20being%20dismantled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20the%20goggles%20co