idual%20portfolio%20managers%20and%20their%20analysts%2C%20is%20something%20many%20could%20do.%20Or%20at%20least%20that's%20the%20belief%20of%20Marc%20Greenberg%2C%20the%20former%20director%20of%20research%20at%20Steve%20Cohen's%20Point72.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreenberg%20launched%20a%20consulting%20firm%20called%20Greener%20Pastures%20that%20works%20with%20smaller%20funds%20on%20talent%20development%20and%20their%20research%20process%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthelongandtheshortofit.substack.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealso%20writes%20a%20substack%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20covers%20the%20%26quot%3Bblock-and-tackle-type%20stuff%26quot%3B%20of%20investing%20at%20a%20multistrategy%20hedge%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20notion%26quot%3B%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20this%20secret%20sauce%20that%20happens%20within%20funds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20saying%20the%20%26quot%3Blore%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20founders%20can%20make%20these%20firms%20seem%20%26quot%3Bmagical%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20the%20PMs%20%26quot%3Bwork%20really%20hard%20and%20know%20their%20companies%20really%20well.%26quot%3B%20His%20writing%20is%20about%20earnings%20prep%2C%20how%20to%20use%20data%2C%20how%20to%20manage%20risk%2C%20and%20how%20to%20do%20fundamental%20research%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20success%20of%20these%20managers%20is%20driven%20by%20%26quot%3Bthe%20men%20and%20the%20women%20in%20the%20seats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreenberg%20is%20part%20of%20a%20group%20of%20former%20investors%20and%20executives%20from%20these%20multistrategy%20funds%20that%20are%20trying%20to%20make%20the%20industry%20more%20accessible%20to%20those%20unfamiliar%20with%20the%20inner%20workings%20of%20a%20Millennium%20or%20a%20Citadel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrett%20Caughran%2C%20a%20former%20portfolio%20manager%20for%20Schonfeld%2C%20Citadel%2C%20and%20D.E.%20Shaw%2C%20founded%20a%20training%20academy%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fundamentedge.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFundamental%20Edge%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%202022%20with%20the%20explicit%20purpose%20of%20training%20young%20people%20in%20finance%20for%20jobs%20at%20multistrategy%20funds.%20Doug%20Garber%2C%20a%20former%20analyst%20at%20Citadel%20and%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20Millennium%2C%20has%20launched%20a%20podcast%20called%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopen.spotify.com%2Fshow%2F4UHbkYE2OJwfhY2MZqGG5Y%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPitch%20the%20PM%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20where%20he%20reviews%20stock%20pitches%20in%20the%20same%20way%20he%20would%20if%20he%20were%20still%20investing%20for%20hedge%20fund%20founders%20Ken%20Griffin%20or%20Izzy%20Englander.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20hedge-fund%20industry%20has%20matured%20and%20more%20capital%20has%20concentrated%20among%20the%20biggest%20players%2C%20there's%20a%20growing%20demand%20for%20talent%20to%20keep%20it%20all%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20talent%20has%20led%20to%20bidding%20wars%20that%20rival%20free%20agency%20in%20major%20sports%20leagues%2C%20as%20Goldman%20Sachs'%20prime%20brokerage%20desk%20notes%20in%20a%20recent%20report%20that%20pass-through%20fees%2C%20which%20cover%20expenses%20like%20bringing%20on%20big%20recruits%2C%20were%204%25%20of%20assets%20in%202024%20%E2%80%94%20a%20jump%20from%203.3%25%20the%20year%20prior.%20In%20a%20recent%20bond%20offering%20prospectus%2C%20Citadel%20notes%20that%20investors%20paid%20%2417%20billion%20in%20pass-through%20fees%20from%202021%20through%20mid-2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20Major%20League%20Baseball's%20New%20York%20Mets%2C%20has%20dealt%20with%20both%2C%20doling%20out%20the%20largest-ever%20deal%20in%20sports%20history%20to%20outfielder%20Juan%20Soto%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2025-01-31%2Fpoint72-lures-marshall-wace-s-liu-with-50-million-pay-package%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20guarantee%20of%20%2450%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20lure%20Marshall%20Wace%20PM%20Kevin%20Liu%20to%20Point72.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20not%20just%20a%20shortage%20of%20top-tier%20talent.%20These%20funds%20need%20more%20young%20analysts%20to%20support%20their%20ever-growing%20ranks%20of%20PMs.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhat%20the%20new%20breed%20of%20consultants%2C%20writers%2C%20and%20podcasters%20are%20doing%20is%20putting%20the%20brands%20of%20the%20biggest%20funds%20on%20the%20radar%20of%20smart%20young%20people%20considering%20their%20next%20move%20%E2%80%94%20and%20laying%20out%20what%20life%20is%20like%20at%20these%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20definitely%20a%20demand%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Garber%20said%2C%20and%20he's%20mentoring%20young%20investors%20in%20college%20and%20leaving%20grad%20programs%20now.%20This%20next%20generation%20is%20eager%20to%20work%20for%20some%20of%20the%20industry's%20biggest%20names%2C%20he%20said%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bthey%20don't%20know%20the%20long-short%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20students%20I%20talk%20to%2C%20they%20want%20Citadel%20or%20Point72%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22588b5893-8659-4ff1-95a5-763ace4d52c7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E750%20students%20and%20counting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20it's%20not%20uncommon%20for%20people%20to%20leave%20hedge%20funds%20%E2%80%94%20which%20often%20recruit%20ambitious%2C%20entrepreneurial%20types%20%E2%80%94%20and%20start%20their%20own%20businesses%2C%20even%20if%20that%20startup%20isn't%20another%20investment%20manager.%20Former%20Point72%20research%20head%20Kirk%20McKeown%20cofounded%20data%20startup%20Carbon%20Arc%20in%202021.%20One-time%20Citadel%20and%20Millennium%20comms%20leader%20Tripp%20Kyle%20and%20former%20AQR%20spokesperson%20Claudia%20Gray%20partnered%20to%20start%20their%20external%20agency%2C%20Northport%20Partners%2C%20in%202023.%20Elliott's%20former%20European%20government%20affairs%20leader%2C%20Claire%20Jolly%2C%20started%20consultancy%20Beaufort%20Strategy%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20those%20businesses%20and%20many%20of%20those%20who%20have%20come%20before%20them%20are%20focused%20on%20serving%20the%20needs%20of%20those%20already%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20not%20looking%20to%20bring%20a%20separate%20universe%20of%20people%20into%20hedge%20funds.%20Greenberg%2C%20Caughran%2C%20and%20Garber%20are%20all%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20speaking%20to%20the%20youngest%20in%20the%20talent%20pool%20and%20increasing%20the%20brand%20recognition%20of%20the%20industry's%20biggest%20managers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20another%20example%20of%20the%20institutionalization%20of%20the%20hedge%20fund%20industry%2C%20which%20has%20grown%20to%20the%20point%20where%20the%20biggest%20managers%20are%20recruiting%20straight%20from%20undergraduate%20programs%20instead%20of%20poaching%20talent%20from%20investment%20banks%20or%20private%20equity.%20Point72%2C%20Citadel%2C%20D.E.%20Shaw%2C%20and%20others%20have%20built%20competitive%2C%20well-paid%20internship%20programs.%20Millennium%20and%20UBS%20have%20a%20partnership%20in%20which%20a%20new%20grad%20for%20the%20hedge%20fund%20would%20spend%20a%20year%20in%20the%20bank's%20equity%20research%20department%20as%20an%20outsourced%20training%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInternal%20training%20programs%20though%20are%20still%20a%20work%20in%20progress%20for%20many%20funds%20and%20talented%20young%20people%20can%20get%20washed%20out%20quickly%2C%20Caughran%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHistorically%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20funds%20expected%20young%20talent%20to%20learn%20through%20osmosis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20struggle%20for%20him%20personally%20when%20he%20first%20got%20to%20the%20buy-side%2C%20though%20he%20started%20his%20investing%20career%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-tree-shows-how-many-tiger-cub-hedge-funds-there-are-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETiger%20Cub%20hedge%20fund%3C%2Fa%3E%20Maverick%20Capital%2C%20not%20a%20multistrategy%20fund.%20Fundamental%20Edge%20already%20has%20had%20750%20students%20take%20its%20various%20training%20courses%20and%20has%20other%20full-time%20instructors%20with%20buy-side%20experience%20reviewing%20everything%20from%20prepping%20for%20earnings%20to%20understanding%20factors%20and%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20lays%20out%20what%20life%20is%20like%20at%20these%20firms%2C%20which%20are%20often%20more%20fast-paced%20than%20the%20managers%20or%20banks%20his%20students%20are%20typically%20working%20at.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20making%20the%20career%20choice%20to%20go%20to%20one%20of%20these%20places%2C%20you%20should%20go%20in%20eyes%20wide%20open%20about%20what%20the%20trade-offs%20and%20benefits%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirms%2C%20in%20general%2C%20have%20also%20become%20more%20transparent%2C%20in%20part%20to%20attract%20more%20people%20to%20their%20managers%20and%20improve%20their%20brand%20recognition.%20Cohen%20has%20spoken%20about%20investing%20and%20career%20growth%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-cohen-advice-investing-sports-require-discipline-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20a%20company-run%20podcast%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Griffin%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fcitadel-securities_ken-griffin-at-the-university-of-cambridge-activity-7290029730680983553-vzuF%2F%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_medium%3Dmember_desktop%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecently%20met%20with%3C%2Fa%3E%20Cambridge%20University%20students%20and%20gave%20advice%20on%20what%20they%20should%20do%20after%20graduation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20advent%20of%20Substacks%20like%20Greenberg's%20and%20podcasts%20like%20Garber's%20only%20increases%20awareness%20of%20these%20firms%20and%20what%20they're%20like%20from%20an%20insider's%20perspective.%3C%2