%20I%20wish%20the%20team%20all%20the%20best.%20Like%20we%20won%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20we%20want%20them%20to%20get%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohammad%20Azharuddin%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Rohit's%20retirement%20rumours%2C%20Azharuddin%20said%3A%C2%A0%26quot%3BIt's%20up%20to%20him%20.%20All%20these%20decisions%20are%20best%20left%20for%20the%20individual.%20Many%20people%20say%20'%3Cem%3Eabhi%20retire%20ho%20jao%3C%2Fem%3E'.%20The%20player%20who%20plays%20know%20how%20intense%20his%20feeling%20for%20the%20game%20is.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit's%20Test%20form%20took%20a%20huge%20nosedive%20during%20the%202024-25%20Test%20season%2C%20scoring%20just%20164%20runs%20in%20eight%20matches%20and%2015%20innings%20at%20an%20average%20of%2010.93%2C%20including%2031%20runs%20in%20six%20innings%20against%20Australia%20during%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%20away%20from%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20ODIs%2C%20he%20has%20been%20a%20force%20to%20be%20reckoned%20with%20since%202023.%20Always%20a%20white-ball%20giant%2C%20Rohit's%20ODI%20form%20went%20a%20notch%20as%20he%20mixed%20powerplay%20aggression%20with%20consistency%2C%20scoring%201%2C533%20runs%20in%2032%20matches%20and%2031%20innings%20at%20an%20average%20of%2052.86%20at%20a%20massive%20strike%20rate%20of%20119.76%2C%20with%20three%20centuries%20and%2011%20fifties.%20His%20best%20score%20is%20131.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ninth%20edition%20of%20the%20ICC%20Men's%20Champions%20Trophy%20is%20set%20to%20take%20place%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20from%20February%2019%20to%20March%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eight-team%20tournament%20will%20feature%2015%2050-over%20matches%20and%20will%20be%20played%20across%20Pakistan%20and%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20match%20of%20the%20tournament%20between%20two%20arch-rivals%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20will%20be%20played%20on%20February%2023%20in%20Dubai.%20Indi