ion.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20leaving%20for%20the%20US%20today%20and%20BJP%20sources%20have%20said%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20of%20the%20new%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20held%20after%20his%20return.%20To%20mark%20its%20capital%20comeback%20after%2026%20years%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20organise%20a%20grand%20oath%20event%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%20Chief%20Ministers%20of%20all%20NDA-ruled%20states%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20invited%20to%20the%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739193480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Frp19pdno_delhi-women-mla-split_625x300_10_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-election-2025-delhi-chief-minister-delhis-next-chief-minister-a-woman-murmurs-amid-big-bjp-brainstorm-7677968%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20has%20been%20two%20days%20since%20the%20BJP%20scored%20a%20thumping%20victory%20in%20the%20Delhi%20election%2C%20ending%20the%20AAP's%20decade-long%20rule%20in%20the%20capital.%20With%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20yet%20to%20announce%20its%20Chief%20Minister%20choice%2C%20multiple%20names%20are%20doing%20the%20rounds%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-election-2025-delhi-chief-minister-delhis-next-chief-minister-a-woman-murmurs-amid-big-bjp-brainstorm-7677968%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22McDonald's%20sees%20biggest%20drop%20in%20US%20sales%20in%20Q4%20in%20nearly%20five%20years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739193451000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fmcdonald-s-sees-biggest-drop-in-us-sales-in-q4-in-nearly-five-years-125021001105_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20fell%201.4%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20US%2C%20McDonald's%20biggest%20market%2C%20its%20steepest%20drop%20since%20the%20COVID-19%20pa