2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc3e1kne7q1qo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20French%20president%20posted%20a%20montage%20of%20parodies%20featuring%20himself%20to%20promote%20an%20AI%20Summit%20in%20Paris.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc3e1kne7q1qo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc3e1kne7q1qo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc3e1kne7q1qo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20How%20The%20Middle%20Class%20Turned%20Delhi's%20Fate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202018%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20inaugurated%20the%20spanking%20new%20headquarters%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20Delhi.%20Since%20then%2C%20he%20has%20travelled%20many%20times%20to%20the%20imposing%20building%20in%20Deen%20Dayal%20Upadhyay%20Marg%20to%20celebrate%20the%20electoral%20victories%20of%20the%20BJP.%20Television%20channels%20have%20shown%20visuals%20of%20myriad%20leaders%20with%20broad%20smiles%20waiting%20for%20him%20to%20address%20the%20jubilant%20crowd%20of%20BJP%20supporters.%20They%20did%20the%20same%20on%20February%208%20as%20the%20cadre%20and%20leaders%20prepared%20for%20Modi%20to%20arrive%20to%20celebrate%20the%20BJP's%20victory%20in%20Delhi%2C%20a%20state%20it%20had%20last%20won%20in%201993.%20But%20the%20authors%20did%20notice%20something.%20This%20time%2C%20many%20TV%20cameras%20focused%20on%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%2C%20who%20sported%20her%20trademark%20smile%3A%20seemingly%20reluctant%2C%20enigmatic%20and%20yet%20interesting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOvernight%20Perception%20Change%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20why%20not%3F%20Even%20before%20she%20presented%20her%20eighth%20budget%20on%20February%201%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20already%20been%20giving%20a%20tough%20fight%20to%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP).%20However%2C%20scores%20of%20surveys%20done%20by%20C%20Voter%20since%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20of%202024%20had%20indicated%20that%20the%20middle-class%20voter%20of%20India%20had%20not%20just%20been%20in%20despair%20but%20also%20quite%20dissatisfied%20with%20the%20government%20at%20the%20Centre.%20All%20that%20disappeared%20literally%20overnight%20when%20Sitharaman%20announced%20a%20massive%20tax%20bonanza%20for%20India's%20middle%20class.%20It%20was%20akin%20to%20pulling%20a%20rabbit%20out%20of%20a%20hat.%20Prior%20to%20the%20budget%20speech%2C%20about%2030%25%20of%20respondents%20in%20the%20C%20Voter%20Tracker%20survey%20had%20said%20that%20they%20expected%20their%20quality%20of%20life%20to%20improve%20in%20the%20next%20year%2C%20while%20more%20than%2037%25%20expected%20it%20to%20deteriorate.%20The%20budget%2C%20however%2C%20had%20a%20near-magical%20impact%20on%20middle-class%20perceptions.%20The%20tracker%20survey%20results%20of%20February%202%20were%20revealing.%20While%2024%25%20expected%20their%20quality%20of%20life%20to%20deteriorate%20in%20the%20next%20year%2C%20more%20than%2040%25%20expected%20it%20to%20improve.%20There%20can%20be%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20final%20BJP%20push%20for%20victory%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20the%20Delhi%20campaign%20was%20powered%20by%20the%20middle%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EA%20Four-Point%20Gap%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20face%20of%20it%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20delivered%20a%20landslide%20win%20in%20Delhi.%20From%20eight%20in%202020%2C%20the%20seat%20tally%20went%20to%2048%2C%20while%20AAP's%20score%20crashed%20to%2022%20from%2062%20in%202020.%20But%20numbers%20can%20be%20deceptive.%20One%20major%20expectation%20of%20commentators%20was%20that%20the%20Congress%20would%20dent%20AAP%20big%20time%20in%20quite%20a%20number%20of%20seats%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20party%20campaigned%20stridently%20and%20aggressively%20against%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20despite%20the%20two%20being%20members%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20data%20from%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20suggests%20that%20the%20Congress%20vote%20share%20improved%20marginally%20to%20a%20little%20over%206%25.%20That's%20why%20the%20vote%20share%20of%20AAP%20is%20still%20formidable%E2%80%94almost%2044%25%E2%80%94despite%20such%20a%20heavy%20loss.%20In%20most%20other%20states%20in%20India%2C%20a%2044%25%20vote%20share%20would%20be%20enough%20to%20win%20a%20big%20majority.%20But%20it's%20also%20true%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20together%20managed%20to%20gather%20almost%2048%25%20votes.%20That%204%20percentage%20point%20divergence%20proved%20decisive%20in%20the%20end%20and%20spelt%20electoral%20doom%20for%20AAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EResentment%2C%20But%20Not%20Absolute%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20vote%20share%20jump%20came%20largely%20from%20middle-class%20voters%2C%20who%20had%20been%20in%20the%20habit%20of%20voting%20en%20bloc%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20siding%20with%20AAP%20in%20assembly%20elections.%20That%20is%20why%20the%20BJP%20and%20AAP%20each%20won%20more%20than%2050%25%20of%20the%20vote%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20assembly%20elections%2C%20respectively.%20This%20dichotomy%20was%20broken%20this%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20there%20was%20considerable%20anger%20among%20Delhi%20voters%20because%20of%20the%20dismal%20conditions%20of%20roads%2C%20open%20drainages%20and%20overflowing%20sewers%2C%20poor%20drinking%20water%2C%20pollution%20and%20many%20other%20civic%20issues.%20Yet%2C%20unlike%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20of%202014%20or%20even%20the%20West%20Bengal%20assembly%20elections%20of%202011%2C%20there%20was%20no%20tidal%20wave%20of%20anger%20and%20resentment%20as%20such.%20Do%20recall%20that%20most%20political%20parties%20would%20kill%20to%20get%20a%2044%25%20vote%20share%20in%20any%20election.%20AAP%20has%20done%20that.%20So%2C%20the%20data%20clearly%20indicates%20that%20while%20a%20section%20of%20the%20poorer%20voters%20did%20switch%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20most%20stayed%20loyal%20to%20AAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Classic%20'Class'%20Election%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20a%20classic%20%E2%80%9Cclass%E2%80%9D%20election.%20While%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdisadvantaged%E2%80%9D%20class%20stayed%20with%20AAP%2C%20the%20middle%20class%20and%20the%20rich%20switched%20en%20masse%20to%20the%20BJP.%20It%20would%20also%20be%20important%20to%20remember%20here%20that%20the%20income%20levels%20of%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Cmiddle%20class%E2%80%9D%20cannot%20be%20compared%20to%20the%20middle%20class%20in%20states%20like%20Bihar%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20West%20Bengal%20or%20Odisha.%20For%20instance%2C%20even%20the%20lowest-skilled%20worker%20employed%20as%2C%20say%2C%20a%20domestic%20help%20in%20upper-middle-class%20families%20in%20Delhi%2C%20manages%20to%20earn%20a%20total%20monthly%20income%20of%20around%20Rs%2012%2C000%20at%20the%20very%20least.%20The%20total%20household%20income%20of%20such%20workers%20would%20be%20much%20more%20than%20the%20incomes%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpoor%E2%80%9D%20households%20in%2C%20say%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Bihar%2C%20West%20Bengal%20or%20Odisha.%20Thus%2C%20quite%20a%20few%20of%20these%20aspirational%20middle-class%20voters%20in%20Delhi%20did%20shift%20to%20the%20BJP%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarring%20the%20Rs%203%2C000-6%2C000%20family%20income%20group%2C%20most%20poor%20voters%20of%20Delhi%20have%20remained%20loyal%20to%20AAP.%20The%20reason%20for%20this%20%E2%80%9Caberration%E2%80%9D%20could%20be%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20Delhi%20citizens%20earn%20more%20than%20that%20and%20also%20get%20benefits%20like%20free%20ration%20and%20food%20under%20the%20Centre's%20schemes.%20In%20Delhi%2C%20those%20earning%20between%20Rs%206%2C000%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20a%20month%20would%20be%20considered%20really%20poor.%20In%20this%20category%2C%20AAP%20has%20enjoyed%20a%2010%25%20vote%20share%20edge.%20Among%20middle-class%20Delhi%20folks%20earning%20between%20Rs%2050%2C000%20to%20Rs%201%20lakh%20a%20month%20(there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20them%20in%20Delhi%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Central%20and%20state%20government%20employees%20and%20salaried%20people%20in%20the%20private%20sector)%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20enjoyed%20a%20vote%20share%20edge%20of%2022%25%20over%20AAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20Can't%20Slow%20Down%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20just%20about%20sums%20up%20the%20Delhi%20election.%20AAP%20has%20not%20been%20wiped%20out%20the%20way%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20Delhi%20in%202015.%20It%20still%20has%20the%20support%20of%20about%2044%25%20of%20Delhi%20voters.%20The%20BJP%20juggernaut%20is%20likely%20to%20keep%20rolling%20to%20pare%20down%20this%20figure%20as%20well.%20Nonetheless%2C%20this%20time%2C%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20seems%20to%20have%20delivered%20the%20perfect%20knock-out%20punch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Yashwant%20Deshmukh%20is%20the%20Founder%20%26amp%3B%20Editor-in-Chief%20of%20CVoter%20Foundation%20and%20Sutanu%20Guru%20is%20Executive%20Director)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739192940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fjk2s7078_bjp-celebrates-delhi-election-results_625x300_08_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-the-middle-class-turned-delhis-fate-7678035%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20has%20been%20a%20classic%20%26quot%3Bclass%26quot%3B%20election.%20While%20the%20%26quot%3Bdisadvantaged%26quot%3B%20class%20stayed%20with%20AAP%2C%20the%20middle%20class%20and%20the%20rich%20switched%20en%20masse%20to%20the%20BJP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fho