e-at-a-high-stakes-ai-summit-in-paris%2Famp_articleshow%2F118120489.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saudi%20Drama%20Against%20The%20Patriarchy%20%E2%80%98Hobal%E2%80%99%20Beats%20Hollywood%20Titles%20Becoming%20Fast-Growing%20Local%20Hit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739192648000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FHobal.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236302356%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Saudi%20filmmaker%C2%A0Abdulaziz%20Alshlahei%E2%80%99s%20drama%20%E2%80%9CHobal%E2%80%9D%20about%20clashes%20between%20tradition%20and%20modernity%20within%20a%20Saudi%20family%20during%20the%20early%201990s%20is%20scoring%C2%A0mightily%20at%20the%20Saudi%20Arabian%20box%20office%2C%20outperfoming%20Hollywood%20titles%20such%20as%20%E2%80%9CMufasa%3A%20The%20Lion%20King%2C%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CFlight%20Risk%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CDen%20of%20Thieves%202%3A%20Pantera.%E2%80%9D%20The%20timely%20film%20in%20which%20a%20Saudi%20family%20is%20forced%20by%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Nvivarelli%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2025%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fsaudi-drama-patriarchy-hobal-hollywood-fast-growing-hit-1236302356%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20Told%20To%20Talk%20To%20'Gavaskar%2C%20Dravid'%20As%20Poor%20Form%20Continues%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20stunned%20expression%20after%20he%20was%20adjudged%20caught%20behind%20via%20DRS%20in%20the%20second%20India%20vs%20England%20ODI%20would%20be%20etched%20for%20a%20long%20time%20in%20Indian%20fans'%20memories.%20Over%20the%20past%20three%20months%2C%20the%20question%20marks%20on%20Virat%20Kohli's%20future%20have%20increased.%20One%20of%20the%20greats%20in%20modern%20day%20cricket%2C%20Kohli%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20fire%20according%20to%20his%20potential.%20In%20the%202024-25%20Border%20Gavaskar%20Trophy%2C%20barring%20one%20century%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20was%20mostly%20off-colour.%20Then%2C%20he%20missed%20the%20first%20ODI%20against%20England%20due%20to%20an%20injury%20before%20being%20picked%20for%20the%20second%20ODI.%20However%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20could%20score%20only%20five%20off%20eight%20balls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli's%20current%20form%20is%20bound%20to%20raise%20India's%20headache%20ahead%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025.%20Sri%20Lanka's%201996%20World%20Cup-winning%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Arjuna%20Ranatunga%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F41531-arjuna-ranatunga-playerprofile%5C%22%3EArjuna%20Ranatunga%3C%2Fa%3E%20believes%20that%20Kohli%20must%20seek%20help%20for%20India%20greats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20what%20Kohli%20needs%20to%20do%20is%20speak%20to%20people%20like%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40594-sunil-manohar-gavaskar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Dilip%20Vengsarkar%20or%20a%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That's%20what%20he%20can%20do.%20They%20can%20certainly%20help%20him%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Arjuna%20Ranatunga%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fvirat-kohli-needs-to-speak-to-people-like-sunil-gavaskar-or-rahul-dravid-former-sri-lanka-captain-arjuna-ranatunga%2Fcid%2F2082607%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Saturday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanatunga%2C%20however%2C%20dismissed%20question%20marks%20over%20Kohli's%20future%20in%20international%20cricket.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20player%20like%20Kohli%20who%20has%20scored%20so%20much%20of%20runs%2C%20I%20feel%20it's%20best%20if%20that's%20left%20to%20him.%20It's%20a%20call%20that%20Kohli%20needs%20to%20take%2C%20so%20let%20him%20take%20it.%20Why%20always%20have%20the%20spotlight%20on%20him%3F%20It's%20quite%20unnecessary%20I%20feel.%20It's%20his%20decision%2C%20so%20let%20him%20take%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Ranatunga%2C%20who%20has%20played%20Sri%20Lanka%20in%2093%20Tests%20and%20269%20ODIs%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20their%20stature%20and%20the%20kind%20of%20batsmen%20they%20have%20been%2C%20I%20feel%20it's%20a%20matter%20of%20one%20good%20innings%20to%20regain%20their%20rhythm.%20Let's%20see.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Kohli%20failed%20to%20fire%20in%C2%A0%20the%20first%20ODI%2C%20Rohit%20scored%20a%20brilliant%20century.%20Former%20England%20star%20player%20Kevin%20Pietersen%20believes%20that%20one%20good%20innings%20will%20go%20them%20world%20of%20good%20in%20terms%20of%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFormer%20players%2C%20who%20are%20working%20as%20commentators%2C%20often%20say%20that%20a%20struggling%20player%20needs%20one%20good%20shot%20to%20return%20to%20form%2C%20but%20I%20think%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20one%20good%20innings.%20Players%20like%20Virat%20and%20Rohit%20would%20like%20to%20win%20a%20match%20for%20their%20country%20rather%20than%20playing%20good%20strokes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20player%20is%20able%20to%20remain%20not%20out%2C%20he%20can%20say%20that%20his%20form%20has%20returned.%20Virat%20and%20Rohit%20would%20want%20to%20raise%20their%20arms%20to%20thank%20the%20fans%20for%20backing%20them.%20Everyone%20is%20hitting%20sixes%20these%20days%2C%20but%20as%20a%20player%2C%20you%20want%20to%20win%20matches.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739192640000%2C%2