6quot%3B.%20After%20INDIA%20ally%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Chief%20Minister%20Omar%20Abdullah's%20%26quot%3BAur%20lado%20apas%20mein%20(keep%20fighting%20among%20yourselves)%26quot%3B%20jibe%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20Shiv%20Sena%20has%20pointed%20fingers%20at%20the%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20for%20the%20Delhi%20defeat.%20And%20in%20Bengal%2C%20concerns%20are%20surfacing%20in%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20Congress%20over%20a%20Congress%20action%20replay%20in%20the%20state%20elections%20due%20next%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20disunity%20and%20discord%20among%20opposition%20parties%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Maharashtra%20directly%20aided%20the%20BJP%20in%20its%20victory%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20an%20editorial%20Sena%20UBT%20mouthpiece%20%26quot%3BSaamna%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Delhi%2C%20both%20the%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress%20fought%20to%20destroy%20each%20other%2C%20making%20the%20victory%20easier%20for%20the%20BJP.%20If%20this%20continues%2C%20why%20even%20form%20alliances%3F%20Just%20fight%20to%20your%20heart's%20content...%20Just%20keep%20fighting%20among%20yourself%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%20Saamna%20editorial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20born%20out%20of%20Anna%20Hazare's%20anti-corruption%20movement%20that%20was%20instrumental%20in%20ending%20the%20Congress%20rule%20in%20Delhi%20and%20the%20Centre%2C%20grew%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party.%20So%20it%20raised%20eyebrows%20when%20the%20need%20to%20keep%20the%20BJP%20out%20got%20both%20parties%20on%20the%20same%20platform%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20polls%20over%2C%20both%20parties%20had%20reverted%20to%20their%20antagonistic%20stance%2C%20which%20only%20escalated%20when%20the%20votes%20in%20Delhi%20were%20at%20stake.%20It%20came%20as%20no%20surprise%20that%20the%20Congress%20hugely%20ate%20into%20AAP's%20non-BJP%20votes%20that%20contributed%20to%20AAP's%20defeat%20in%20a%20number%20of%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20that%2C%20despite%20the%20Congress's%20zero%20score%20in%20Delhi%20in%20the%20third%20straight%20election%2C%20leaders%20of%20the%20party%2C%20in%20public%20and%20private%2C%20expressed%20satisfaction%20over%20AAP's%20defeat%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20dismay%20in%20the%20Opposition%20camp.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20election%2C%20many%20had%20pointed%20out%20that%20had%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress%20joined%20hands%20instead%2C%20their%20combined%20strength%20would%20have%20been%20enough%20to%20keep%20the%20BJP%20out%20of%20power%20in%20Delhi%20yet%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20to%20point%20this%20out%20was%20Omar%20Abdullah%2C%20who%20is%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20in%20his%20state%20with%20his%20%26quot%3BAur%20lado%26quot%3B%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Samajwadi%20Party%20leader%20Ram%20Gopal%20Yadav%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20having%20a%20%26quot%3Bbad%20attitude%26quot%3B%20and%20questioned%20why%20they%20were%20attacking%20AAP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20shrugged%20off%20the%20accusations%2C%20arguing%20that%20it%20was%20AAP%20which%20did%20not%20want%20any%20alliance%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20had%20spelt%20it%20out%20ahead%20of%20the%20election%20while%20announcing%20candidates%20for%20Delhi's%2070%20seats.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bengal%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20there%20is%20concern%20whether%20the%20Congress%20would%20cut%20votes%20in%20the%20coming%20election%2C%20which%2C%20many%20say%20would%20be%20a%20tough%20one%20for%20Mamata%20Banerjee.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20Ms%20Banerjee%20has%20assured%20her%20party%20MLAs%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20not%20a%20challenge%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20is%20enough%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20she%20also%20remarked%20that%20AAP%20did%20not%20help%20the%20Congress%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Congress%20did%20not%20help%20the%20AAP%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739188620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fjnm1brd_uddhav-thackeray_625x300_31_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-even-form-alliances-sena-mouthpiece-saamna-chides-congress-aap-7678259%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20role%20in%20the%20defeat%20of%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20in%20the%20recently%20concluded%20Delhi%20Assembly%20election%20is%20ballooning%20before%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%2C%20which%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20Revanth%20Reddy%20described%20today%20as%20%26quot%3Bfractured%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-even-form-alliances-sena-mouthpiece-saamna-chides-congress-aap-7678259%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20says%20US%20is%20'committed%20to%20buying%20and%20owning%20Gaza'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739188597000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F92fd%2Flive%2F8f11e400-e7a1-11ef-8593-65a781785cd6.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcn57neepx4vo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20has%20been%20global%20condemnation%20of%20his%20plan%20to%20take%20over%20the%20strip%20and%20move%20its%20Palestinians%20out.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A316%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcn57neepx4vo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcn57neepx4vo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcn57neepx4vo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alliance%20or%20go%20solo%3F%20Cong%20leaders%20urge%20party%20to%20decide%20strategy%20after%20Delhi%20deb