ems-frequent-traveler-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elonger%20Amtrak%20train%20ride%3C%2Fa%3E%20here%20in%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20where%20delays%20can%20be%20somewhat%20common%20%E2%80%94%20I%20had%20no%20such%20concerns%20in%20booking%20my%20500-kilometer%20(311-mile)%20Shinkansen%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20atmosphere%20on%20the%20train%20was%20very%20peaceful.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20of%20a%20bullet%20train%20with%20rows%20of%20two%20seats%20on%20either%20side%20of%20aisle%20with%20storage%20above%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a36c26bfebcc4d029dcf57%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20train%20felt%20quiet%20and%20peaceful.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Adler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20boarding%20our%20train%20car%2C%20I%20was%20struck%20by%20how%20tranquil%20it%20felt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20no%20loud%20phone%20calls%2C%20no%20seat-kicking%20toddlers%20%E2%80%94%20just%20the%20sounds%20of%20hushed%20talking%20and%20some%20scraping%20noises%20as%20we%20placed%20our%20carry-ons%20above%20our%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20felt%20very%20different%20from%20the%20experiences%20I've%20had%20on%20American%20trains%2C%20which%20are%20generally%20much%20noisier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEach%20train%20car%20had%20designated%20spots%20for%20storing%20larger%20luggage%2C%20although%20these%20must%20be%20reserved%20in%20advance.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Luggage%20storage%20area%20behind%20seats%20on%20bullet%20train%20in%20Japan%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a36c267bb3f854015bc8b3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20didn't%20reserve%20space%20for%20our%20larger%20luggage%20because%20we%20didn't%20feel%20like%20lugging%20it%20around.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Adler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2