20said%20that%20while%20he%20had%20not%20watched%20the%20video%20clip%2C%20anyone%20who%20crosses%20the%20limits%20of%20decency%20will%20face%20action.%20Two%20Mumbai%20lawyers%20have%20already%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20Allahbadia%2C%20better%20known%20as%20the%20BeerBiceps%20Guy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20informed%20about%20this%2C%20though%20I%20have%20not%20watched%20it%20yet.%20I%20came%20to%20know%20that%20it%20was%20very%20vulgar%20and%20this%20was%20wrong.%20Everyone%20has%20freedom%20of%20speech%20but%20this%20freedom%20ends%20when%20we%20encroach%20upon%20others'%20freedom.%20Everyone%20has%20limits%2C%20if%20anyone%20crosses%20them%2C%20action%20will%20be%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Mumbai%3A%20On%20controversy%20over%20YouTuber%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia's%20remarks%20on%20a%20show%2C%20Maharashtra%20CM%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20come%20to%20know%20about%20it.%20I%20have%20not%20seen%20it%20yet.%20Things%20have%20been%20said%20and%20presented%20in%20a%20wrong%20way.%20Everyone%20has%20freedom%20of%20speech%20but%20our%20freedom%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FyXKcaWJWDD%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FyXKcaWJWDD%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1888846803245957457%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2010%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeking%20an%20FIR%20against%20Allahbadia%20and%20other%20comics%2C%20lawyers%20Ashish%20Rai%20and%20Pankaj%20Mishra%20have%20written%20to%20Mumbai%20Police%20Commissioner%20Vivek%20Phalsankar%20and%20the%20state%20women's%20commission%2C%20flagging%20how%20remarks%20made%20on%20'India's%20Got%20Latent'%20show%20amount%20to%20disrespecting%20women%20and%20must%20attract%20action.%20The%20complaint%20names%20Allahabadia%2C%20comics%20Samay%20Raina%20and%20Apoorva%20Makhija%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20short%20clip%20from%20the%20show%2C%20which%20is%20now%20viral%2C%20shows%20Allahbadia%20asking%20a%20contestant%2C%20%26quot%3BWould%20you%20rather%20watch%20your%20parents%20have%20sex%20every%20day%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20life%20or%20join%20in%20once%20and%20stop%20it%20forever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20says%20the%20comics%20made%20objectionable%20remarks%20about%20women's%20bodies.%20Their%20remarks%20were%20spreading%20vulgar%20thoughts%20in%20children's%20minds%20about%20their%20parents%2C%20says%20the%20complaint.%20Such%20statements%20were%20made%20with%20the%20sole%20purpose%20of%20making%20money%2C%20the%20lawyers%20have%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20demanded%20that%20the%20'India's%20Got%20Latent'%20show%20be%20shut%20down%20and%20a%20case%20registered%20against%20the%20comics%20and%20the%20show's%20organisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Allahbadia's%20remarks%20triggered%20massive%20outrage%20on%20social%20media%2C%20with%20many%20claiming%20vulgarity%20was%20being%20passed%20off%20as%20comedy%20in%20shows%20such%20as%20'India's%20Got%20Latent'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20to%20speak%20out%20is%20journalist%20and%20lyricist%20Neelesh%20Misra.%20Sharing%20a%20clip%20of%20Allahbadia's%20remark%2C%20he%20said%20creators%20of%20the%20platform%20have%20%26quot%3Bzero%20sense%20of%20responsibility%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20also%20not%20surprised%20at%20all%20that%20four%20people%20at%20the%20desk%20-%20and%20lots%20in%20the%20audience%20-%20celebrated%20this%20and%20had%20a%20great%20laugh.%20You%2C%20the%20audience%2C%20normalised%20and%20celebrated%20this%20and%20people%20like%20these%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDecency%20is%20not%20incentivised%20in%20India%20-%20by%20platforms%20or%20audiences%20-%20and%20creators%20are%20stooping%20lower%20and%20lower%20for%20audience%20reach%20and%20revenue.%20Banal%2C%20crass%2C%20insensitive%20are%20words%20only%20for%20boring%20uncool%20people.%20These%20creators%20can%20say%20anything%20in%20the%20name%20of%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20get%20away%20with%20it.%20Again%2C%20meet%20the%20creators%20who%20are%20shaping%20our%20country's%20creative%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Misra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Supriya%20Shrinate%20said%20the%20fact%20that%20such%20comments%20draw%20applause%20must%20worry%20us.%20%26quot%3BThis%20isn't%20creative.%20It's%20pervert.%20And%20we%20can't%20normalise%20perverse%20behaviour%20as%20cool.%20The%20fact%20that%20this%20sick%20comment%20met%20loud%20applause%20must%20worry%20us%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20massive%20row%2C%20Allahbadia%20has%20apologised%20for%20his%20comments%20and%20said%20%26quot%3Bcomedy%20is%20not%20my%20forte%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bit%20wasn't%20cool%26quot%3B.%C2%A0The%2031-year-old%20posted%20an%20apology%20message%20on%20X%20with%20the%20caption%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20shouldn't%20have%20said%20what%20I%20said%20on%20India's%20got%20latent.%20I'm%20sorry.%26quot%3B%C2%A0In%20the%20video%20message%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20comment%20wasn't%20just%20inappropriate%2C%20it%20was%20not%20even%20funny.%20Comedy%20is%20not%20my%20forte%2C%20I%20am%20just%20here%20to%20say%20sorry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739186100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fsq2vk6j_ranveer-allahabadia_625x300_29_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Franveer-allahbadia-samay-raina-spreading-vulgarity-complaint-filed-against-youtuber-ranveer-allahbadia-7676095%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20row%20over%20th