ir%2C%20a%20veteran%20of%20over%20200%20international%20matches%20for%20India%20and%20someone%20who%20was%20instrumental%20in%20India%20winning%20two%20World%20Cup%20finals%2C%20and%20who%20captained%20and%20mentored%20the%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20to%20a%20cumulative%20three%20IPL%20titles%2C%20experienced%20exactly%20that%2C%20the%20hard%20way.%20From%20the%20time%20he%20took%20over%20the%20reins%20of%20the%20team%2C%20which%20also%20has%20cricketers%20he%20himself%20played%20with%2C%20like%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20the%20Indian%20team%20ship%20hit%20some%20rather%20choppy%20waters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECoach%20vs%20Player%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20point%20pretending%20that%20everyone%20was%20happy%20with%20Gautam's%20appointment%20as%20India%20head%20coach.%20Eyebrows%20were%20raised.%20After%20all%2C%20he%20didn't%20have%20any%20coaching%20experience.%20Some%20former%20cricketers%20pointed%20out%20that%20there%20is%20a%20big%20difference%20between%20being%20a%20mentor%20and%20coaching%20an%20international%20cricket%20team.%20The%20critics%20were%20armed%20with%20an%20extra%20dose%20of%20vitriol%20when%20the%20team%20experienced%20historic%20lows%20like%20losing%20a%20bilateral%20ODI%20series%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%2027%20years%2C%20being%20whitewashed%20in%20a%20three-Test%20series%20at%20home%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20and%20then%2C%20of%20course%2C%20relinquishing%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20trophy%20after%20a%20decade.%20But%20though%20he%20found%20himself%20in%20the%20eye%20of%20a%20storm%20of%20scathing%20criticism%2C%20the%20one%20thing%20that%20didn't%20change%20was%20his%20no-nonsense%20approach%20towards%20the%20game%E2%80%94this%20time%20as%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20don't%20take%20into%20account%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20top-level%20athletes%20is%20that%20almost%20all%20of%20them%20have%20their%20own%2C%20extremely%20individual%20style%20of%20approaching%20the%20game%2C%20and%20it's%20almost%20always%20set%20in%20stone.%20That%20style%20and%20the%20way%20they%20tackle%20difficult%20situations%20is%20what%20gave%20them%20incomparable%20success%20as%20active%20athletes.%20How%20can%20one%20realistically%20expect%20someone%20to%20change%20his%20or%20her%20core%20personality%20just%20because%20they%20are%20now%20coach%20and%20not%20a%20player%3F%20That%20just%20does%20not%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Rough%20Start%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGautam%20took%20over%20as%20India%20head%20coach%20right%20after%20the%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup%20title%20win.%20The%20level%20of%20euphoria%20was%20high.%20Rahul%20Dravid%2C%20a%20very%20different%20kind%20of%20personality%2C%20had%20taken%20the%20team%20to%20the%20final%20of%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20and%20the%202024%20T20%20World%20title.%20The%20period%20of%20adjustment%2C%20of%20familiarising%20oneself%20with%20how%20things%20are%20inside%20the%20dressing%20room%2C%20therefore%20will%20be%20a%20longer%20one%20for%20Gautam.%20It%20would%20be%20fair%20to%20say%20that%20he%20was%20predominantly%20approached%20to%20take%20over%20as%20coach%20because%20of%20his%20track%20record%20of%20getting%20results%20with%20KKR.%20When%20similar%20results%20didn't%20materialise%20for%20the%20Indian%20team%2C%20understandably%2C%20the%20reaction%20of%20many%20fans%20was%20to%20say%20that%20the%20wrong%20man%20had%20been%20given%20the%20job.%20But%20what%20one%20must%20not%20forget%20is%20that%20it's%20been%20less%20than%20seven%20months%20since%20he%20took%20over%20as%20coach.%20That's%20not%20a%20very%20long%20time.%20Sometimes%20the%20settling-in%20phase%20is%20longer%20than%20one%20expects.%20I%20spoke%20to%20Mumbai%20cricket%20legend%20Milind%20Rege%20recently%2C%20who%20told%20me%2C%20%E2%80%9CLet's%20give%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20a%20chance.%20Let's%20not%20hang%20him%20so%20early.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20thing%20that%20keeps%20the%20critics%20at%20bay%20though%20is%20success%20on%20the%20field.%20Gambhir%20has%20found%20some%20much-needed%20breathing%20space%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20commanding%204-1%20T20i%20series%20win%20against%20England%20followed%20by%20an%20unbeatable%202-0%20lead%20in%20the%20ongoing%20ODI%20series.%20England%20are%20no%20pushovers%2C%20and%20these%20two%20series%20wins%20have%20somewhat%20restored%20the%20balance.%20Fans%20and%20critics%20will%20have%20to%20pack%20away%20the%20brickbats%20for%20now.%20With%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20around%20the%20corner%2C%20it's%20the%20perfect%20head%20space%20for%20the%20head%20coach%20to%20get%20a%20big%20monkey%20off%20his%20shoulder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh-Stakes%20ODI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20T20i%20series%20win%20was%20another%20reminder%20of%20the%20ruthless%20win%20machine%20that%20the%20Indian%20team%2C%20which%20had%20a%20win%20percentage%20of%20almost%2093%20in%202024%2C%20has%20transformed%20into%2C%20it's%20the%20ODI%20success%20that%20will%20be%20particularly%20sweet%20for%20Gambhir%20and%20Co.%20Not%20just%20because%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20will%20be%20played%20in%20the%20same%20format%2C%20but%20also%20because%20of%20individual%20player%20successes%2C%20something%20that%20significantly%20affects%20the%20overall%20team%20spirit.%20The%20fact%20that%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20has%20found%20some%20much-needed%20form%20is%20a%20huge%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%2C%20not%20just%20for%20Rohit%20the%20batter%2C%20but%20for%20the%20team%20overall.%20A%20captain%20who%20leads%20from%20the%20front%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20inspiring%20things%20in%20a%20cricket%20team.%20Brendon%20McCullum%20brought%20%E2%80%98Bazball'%20to%20the%20England%20Test%20team%2C%20which%20Ben%20Stokes%20welcomed%20and%20incorporated.%20Are%20we%20going%20to%20see%20a%20similar%20script%20play%20out%20in%20Indian%20cricket%3F%20Vice-captain%20Shubman%20Gill%20is%20in%20red-hot%20form%20in%20the%20format%20with%20scores%20of%2087%20and%2060.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20BCCI's%20diktat%20for%20senior%20team%20players%20to%20go%20back%20to%20domestic%20cricket%20got%20a%20huge%20thumbs-up%20from%20Ravindra%20Jadeja.%20The%20all-rounder%2C%20who%20has%20taken%20six%20wickets%20in%20the%20two%20ODIs%20so%20far%2C%20credited%20his%20Ranji%20Trophy%20stint%20against%20Delhi%20recently%2C%20where%20he%20took%2012%20wickets%20in%20the%20match%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%20call%20the%20rhythm%2C%20the%20continuity%2C%20was%20in%20place%20because%20my%20break%20from%20cricket%20wasn't%20that%20long.%E2%80%9D%20That%20will%20be%20music%20to%20the%20ears%20of%20those%20who%20inhabit%20the%20corridors%20of%20power%20in%20Indian%20cricket.%20Shreyas%20Iyer%2C%20who%20managed%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20his%20spot%20in%20the%20ODI%20XI%2C%20is%20looking%20good%20perhaps%20for%20an%20automatic%20spot%2C%20ahead%20of%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20thanks%20to%20his%20scores%20of%2059%20and%2044.%20Varun%20Chakaravarthy%20is%20giving%20the%20selectors%20a%20happy%20problem%20of%20plenty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EProblems%20Persist%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20there%20is%20a%20marked%20distinction%20between%20all%20three%20formats.%20The%20coach%20might%20be%20the%20same%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20personnel%20are%20different.%20Gambhir%20wants%20the%20team%20to%20regularly%20score%20250-260%20in%20T20%20internationals%2C%20and%20it%20looks%20like%20his%20style%20of%20approaching%20the%20game%2C%20which%20is%20essentially%20high-risk%2C%20high-reward%2C%20is%20suiting%20the%20Indian%20T20i%20team%20and%20also%20finally%20seeping%20into%20the%20ODI%20set-up.%20The%20year%202024%20had%20hardly%20any%20ODIs%20for%20Team%20India.%20This%20year%20will%20show%20us%20exactly%20where%20things%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20while%20Gautam%20may%20be%20breathing%20a%20bit%20better%20now%2C%20he%20will%20know%20that%20there's%20still%20work%20left%20to%20do.%20While%20all%20his%20energy%20will%20be%20focused%20on%20the%20ODI%20format%20currently%2C%20with%20one%20eye%20on%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20title%2C%20he%20will%20know%20that%20at%20some%20point%2C%20he%20will%20have%20to%20take%20a%20good%20hard%20look%20at%20the%20Test%20team%2C%20especially%20with%20a%20five-Test%20tour%20of%20England%20coming%20up%20later%20in%20the%20year.%20He%20will%20also%20be%20dearly%20hoping%20that%20Virat%20Kohli%20strikes%20form%20soon%20in%20his%20favourite%20format.%20The%20experiment%2C%20if%20one%20can%20call%20it%20that%2C%20of%20sending%20Axar%20Patel%20in%20at%20No.%205%20is%20working%20for%20now%2C%20but%20KL%20Rahul's%20form%20(two%20and%2010%20in%20the%20two%20ODIs%20so%20far)%2C%20especially%20with%20Rishabh%20Pant%20waiting%20in%20the%20wings%2C%20needs%20to%20be%20considered.%20And%20so%20does%20Jasprit%20Bumrah's%20fitness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20never%20easy%20to%20completely%20mute%20outside%20noise.%20But%20it%20sure%20goes%20down%20multiple%20decibels%20when%20the%20team%20is%20winning.%20The%20coach%20can%20now%20focus%20on%20fixing%20the%20few%20chinks%20in%20the%20ODI%20armour%20as%20the%20team%20eyes%20the%20one%20thing%20that%20silences%20even%20the%20staunchest%20of%20critics%3A%20an%20ICC%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20former%20sports%20editor%20and%20primetime%20sports%20news%20anchor.%20He%20is%20currently%20a%20columnist%2C%20features%20writer%20and%20stage%20actor)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739183820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F955shpj_gautam-gambhir-bcci_625x300_30_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fgautam-gambhir-can-the-coach-silence-his-critics-7677608%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20T20i%2