20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20(Taimur)%20was%20absolutely%20composed.%20He%20was%20fine.%20He%20said%2C%20'I'm%20coming%20with%20you.'%20I%20was%20getting%20a%20lot%20of%20comfort%20just%20from%20looking%20at%20him%20at%20that%20time.%20And%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20go%20alone.%20My%20wife%20sent%20him%20knowing%20what%20he%20would%20do%20for%20me.%20Maybe%20it%20wasn't...%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20it%20was%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do.%20I%20felt%20good%20about%20it.%20And%20I%20also%20thought%2C%20if%20God%20forbid%2C%20something%20happens%2C%20I'd%20like%20for%20him%20to%20be%20there.%20And%20he%20wanted%20to%20be%20there%20also.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%20While%20Saif%20and%20Taimur%20made%20their%20way%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20Kareena%20took%20Jeh%20to%20her%20sister%20Karisma%20Kapoor's%20home.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaif%20recounted%20that%20he%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsaif-ali-khan-makes-first-public-appearance-after-stabbing-incident-feels-nice-to-be-standing-here-7624517%5C%22%3EKareena%20Kapoor%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewere%20asleep%20when%2C%20around%202%20a.m.%2C%20one%20of%20their%20house%20helps%20rushed%20into%20their%20room%2C%20alarmed%20by%20an%20intruder%20demanding%20money%20in%20their%20younger%20son%20Jeh's%20room.%20As%20he%20rushed%20to%20confront%20the%20situation%2C%20Saif%20found%20a%20masked%20man%20standing%20over%20Jeh's%20bed%2C%20wielding%20what%20initially%20appeared%20to%20be%20two%20sticks%20but%20were%20actually%20%26quot%3Bsharp%20hexa%20blades%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomething%20took%20over%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Saif%20recalled%2C%20describing%20how%20he%20instinctively%20grabbed%20the%20intruder%20and%20pulled%20him%20down.%20However%2C%20being%20armed%2C%20the%20attacker%20retaliated%2C%20stabbing%20Saif%20in%20the%20back%20and%20neck%20multiple%20times.%20%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20handle%20it%20after%20a%20while%20as%20there%20were%20two%20knives%20in%20action.%20I%20was%20praying%20that%20someone%20could%20get%20this%20guy%20off%20me%20at%20this%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20shared.%20That's%20when%20his%20house%20help%2C%20Geeta%2C%20stepped%20in%20and%20managed%20to%20pull%20the%20attacker%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaif%20further%20shared%20that%20he%20locked%20the%20intruder%20inside%20Jeh's%20room.%20However%2C%20the%20assailant%20managed%20to%20escape%20the%20same%20way%20he%20had%20entered%20-%20through%20the%20drainpipe%20in%20the%20kids'%20bathroom.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20upon%20reaching%20the%20hospital%20that%20Saif%20grasped%20the%20gravity%20of%20his%20injuries.%20Doctors%20informed%20him%20that%20a%20four-inch%20blade%20had%20penetrated%20his%20shoulder%20blade%2C%20reaching%20close%20to%20his%20spinal%20cord.%20He%20described%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmassive%20stab%2C%26quot%3B%20revealing%20that%20the%20knife%20had%20even%20nicked%20the%20protective%20covering%20of%20his%20spinal%20cord%20which%20caused%20spinal%20fluid%20leakage%20and%20temporary%20numbness%20in%20his%20leg.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20how%20close%20it%20came%20-%20just%20one%20more%20millimetre%2C%20and%20we'd%20be%20talking%20paralysis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaif%20underwent%20an%20extensive%20six-hour%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739169360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fnlqqlt3g_saif_625x300_10_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsaif-ali-khan-on-why-taimur-took-him-to-the-hospital-instead-of-wife-kareena-kapoor-after-knife-attack-my-son-was-composed-7675893%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20also%20thought%2C%20if%20God%20forbid%2C%20something%20happens%2C%20I'd%20like%20for%20him%20to%20be%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Saif%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsaif-ali-khan-on-why-taimur-took-him-to-