dle%20Class%2C%20'Replicants'%20Are%20Coming%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Csmall%3E(Rachel%2C%20a%20'Replicant'%2C%20from%20the%201982%20sci-fi%20thriller%20%3Cstrong%3EBlade%20Runne%3C%2Fstrong%3Er)%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20prime%20minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20who%20passed%20away%20recently%2C%20heralded%20the%20era%20of%20economic%20liberalisation%20in%20India%20with%20the%20quote%3A%20%E2%80%9CNo%20power%20on%20earth%20can%20stop%20an%20idea%20whose%20time%20has%20come.%E2%80%9D%20It%20was%20perhaps%20Singh's%20keen%20sense%20of%20history%20that%20made%20him%20append%20those%20Victor%20Hugo%20lines%20to%20the%20end%20of%20his%20famous%201991%20Budget%20speech%20in%20Parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20forces%20unleashed%20at%20that%20moment%20were%20responsible%20for%20the%20social%2C%20political%20and%20economic%20changes%20that%20marked%20the%20past%2034%20years%20of%20India.%20Economic%20freedom%20helped%20lift%20millions%20out%20of%20poverty.%20It%20made%20wealth%2C%20until%20then%20looked%20down%20upon%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20dubious%20morality%2C%20fashionable.%20Above%20all%2C%20it%20spawned%20a%20vibrant%20middle%20class%20of%20managers%2C%20professionals%2C%20innovators%2C%20entrepreneurs%2C%20creators%2C%20and%20many%20more%20pursuing%20a%20multitude%20of%20new%20vocations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhite-collar%20jobs%2C%20fat%20salaries%2C%20aspirations%2C%20new%20tastes%2C%20and%20uncommon%20pursuits%20drove%20the%20economic%20engine%20for%20three%20decades.%20Conventional%20wisdom%20suggests%20that%20the%20expansion%20of%20this%20class%20helps%20a%20country%20improve%20its%20stock%20in%20the%20world%20in%20many%20ways.%20The%20middle%20class%20greatly%20contributes%20to%20the%20national%20economic%20status%2C%20social%20progress%2C%20and%20transnational%20influence%20with%20their%20creativity%2C%20innovation%2C%20and%20drive.%20Their%20hive%20mind%20powers%20the%20nation%20and%20influences%20its%20trajectory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20time%20for%20another%20idea%E2%80%94Artificial%20Intelligence%20(AI)%E2%80%94has%20arrived%2C%20and%20it%20may%20not%20bode%20well%20for%20the%20middle%20class%2C%20which%20in%20countries%20such%20as%20India%20would%20mean%20the%20very%20backbone%20of%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Disruption%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20phenomenon%2C%20AI%20swept%20the%20public%20imagination%20in%20November%202022%20when%20OpenAI%20unleashed%20ChatGPT%20on%20an%20unsuspecting%20world.%20But%20the%20slow%20creep%20of%20the%20tide%20began%20arguably%20a%20decade%20before%20with%20AlexNet%2C%20an%20artificial%20neural%20architecture%20built%20by%20founders%20Geoffrey%20Hinton%2C%20Alex%20Krishevsky%2C%20and%20Ilya%20Sutskever%2C%20the%20pioneers%20of%20AI%20as%20we%20know%20it.%20What%20they%20demonstrated%20was%20training%20machines%20to%20recognise%20and%20classify%20images.%20That%20was%20made%20possible%20largely%20because%20of%20Nvidia%20re-engineering%20its%20ultra-fast%20graphic%20processing%20units%20built%20for%20gaming%20for%20general-purpose%20computing.%20Its%20programming%20model%20and%20parallel%20computing%20platform%20could%20process%20data%20at%20supercomputer%20speeds.%20Nvidia's%20processors%20kept%20getting%20faster%2C%20each%20generation%20in%20lockstep%20with%20skyrocketing%20demand%20when%20the%20industry%20discovered%20that%20it%20could%20deploy%20the%20processors%20to%20teach%20machines%20how%20to%20analyse%20words%2C%20voice%20and%20images%2C%20still%20and%20moving.%20The%20growth%20of%20the%20industry%20was%20so%20fast%20that%20within%20two%20years%20of%20ChatGPT's%20release%2C%20the%20Nvidia%20stock%20rose%20nearly%20800%25%20in%20value%2C%20helping%20it%20pip%20Apple%20to%20become%20the%20most%20valuable%20company%20in%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeech%20recognition%20and%20medical%20imaging%20arrived%20close%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20AlexNet%20demonstrating%20image%20recognition%2C%20followed%20quickly%20by%20ChatGPT%20and%20generative%20AI%20capable%20of%20creating%20content.%20So%20far%2C%20so%20good.%20It%20is%20from%20the%20next%20iteration%20that%20AI's%20relationship%20with%20humans%20really%20begins%20to%20get%20complicated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelivering%20his%20keynote%20address%20in%20January%20at%20the%20electronics%20trade%20show%2C%20CES%202025%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20Nvidia%20CEO%2C%20Jensen%20Huang%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dk82RwXqZHY8%5C%22%3Eshowed%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20glimpse%20of%20what's%20coming.%20Next%20up%20is%20Agentic%20AI%2C%20which%20can%20perceive%2C%20reason%2C%20plan%20and%20act.%20The%20one%20after%20that%20is%20Physical%20AI%2C%20which%20could%20drive%20vehicles%20and%20make%20general%20robotics%20functional.%20Those%20would%20be%20theoretical%20forerunners%20of%20Replicants%20in%20the%20Harrison%20Ford-starrer%20%3Cem%3EBlade%20Runner%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%201982%20film%20adaptation%20of%20Philip%20K.%20Dick's%20dystopian%20sci-fi%20novel%20%3Cem%3EDo%20Androids%20Dream%20of%20Electric%20Sheep%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Maverick%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk's%20Tesla%20is%20working%20on%20an%20advanced%20generation%20of%20a%20humanoid%20robot%2C%20which%20it%20calls%20Optimus%2C%20that%20displays%20remarkable%20mobility%20skills%20even%20on%20difficult%20terrain%20and%20real-life%20situations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Upending%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20CEO%20David%20Solomon%20described%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20how%20AI%20is%20commoditising%2095%25%20of%20documentation%20work%20that%20now%20takes%20an%20army%20of%20skilled%20executives%20at%20his%20bank%20weeks.%20In%20the%20worst-case%20scenario%2C%20AI%20could%20gut%20Wall%20Street.%20The%20same%20would%20happen%20in%20other%20industries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20scientists%20at%20drugmakers%20or%20metallurgists%20at%20material%20producers%20could%20shrink%20as%20AI-powered%20machines%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fsatyanadella%2Fstatus%2F1879960413082947966%3Fs%3D46%26t%3DfChaSkWo-W69xeWrVHwmyA%5C%22%3Ediscover%3C%2Fa%3E%20drugs%20and%20new%20alloys%20faster.%20A%20skeletal%20group%20of%20engineers%20could%20potentially%20run%20entire%20public%20works%20departments.%20It%20is%20a%20well-recognised%20fact%20that%20factory%20robots%20would%20make%20a%20number%20of%20low-skilled%20jobs%20redundant%2C%20shutting%20out%20one%20conventional%20road%20to%20economic%20progress%20and%20graduation%20to%20the%20middle%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20domino%20effect%20of%20automation%20is%20already%20reflected%20in%20the%20dwindling%20number%20of%20skilled%20workers%20such%20as%20fitters%2C%20welders%2C%20and%20painters%20on%20shop%20floors.%20Past%20technological%20leaps%20such%20as%20steam%20and%20electricity%20produced%20more%20net%20jobs%20and%20better%20wages%20as%20they%20helped%20labour%20productivity%20and%20generated%20new%20tasks.%20Occupations%20that%20spawned%20new%20jobs%20sustained%20jobs%20growth%20in%20the%20post-war%20US%2C%20economists%20Daron%20Acemoglu%20and%20Pascual%20Restrepo%20argued%20in%20a%202019%20paper.%20However%2C%20that%20trend%20is%20trailing%20off.%20Employment%20and%20wage%20growth%20suffered%20in%20the%20first%20two%20decades%20of%20this%20century%20as%20new%20tasks%20failed%20to%20materialise%2C%20they%20wrote.%20And%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20world%2C%20AI%20will%20not%20help%20net%20job%20addition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20these%20rapid%20leaps%20in%20technology%2C%20if%20not%20calibrated%2C%20would%20be%20devastating%2C%20dystopian%20even.%20It%20may%20sound%20alarmist%20but%20intelligent%20robots%20and%20thinking%20systems%20could%20potentially%20clear%20out%20entire%20office%20complexes.%20A%20large%20number%20of%20white-collar%20jobs%20would%20be%20eliminated%20and%20innumerable%20tasks%20commodity-fied.%20The%20requirement%20of%20ancillary%20services%2C%20some%20as%20simple%20as%20fast%20food%20and%20taxis%20near%20offices%2C%20would%20reduce%20as%20a%20result.%20An%20ecosystem%20of%20products%20and%20services%20that%20has%20evolved%20around%20the%20working%20individual%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20Industrial%20Revolution%20would%20undergo%20dramatic%20changes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EHoney%2C%20Shrink%20The%20Middle%20Class%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountries%20such%20as%20India%20will%20struggle%20to%20lift%20people%20out%20of%20poverty%20as%20traditional%20paths%20for%20individual%20economic%20prosperity%20would%20vanish.%20New%20avenues%20might%20open%20up%2C%20but%20those%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20fewer%20and%20require%20early%20investment%20in%20education%20or%20skilling.%20India%20is%20the%20world's%20most%20populous%20country%20and%20youngest%20among%20major%20economies.%20It%20needs%20an%20expanding%20middle%20class%2C%20not%20a%20shrinking%20one.%20Chapter%2013%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Survey%202024-25%20%3C%2Fem%3Eacknowledges%20this%2C%20yet%20bets%20on%20history%3B%20%26quot%3BDemand%20for%20new%20products%20and%20services%20due%20to%20new%20technology%20in%20a%20market%20with%20unmet%20demand%20has%20created%20new%2C%20auxiliary%20tasks%20where%20labour%20has%20a%20competitive%20advantage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20rightly%20proposes%20creating%20stewarding%20institutions%20to%20manage%20the%20disruption%20but%20wrongly%20suggests%20that%20the%20state%20should%20tax%20profits%20generated%20from%20the%20replacement%20of%20labour%20with%20technology%20to%20mobilise%20resources%20if%20companies%20do%20not%20behave%20responsibly.%20This%20is%20not%20to%20say%20that%20companies%20should%20not%20be%20sensitive%20to%20local%20conditions%2C%20but%20taxing%20them%20would%20be%20counterproductive%20and%20will%20result%20in%20them%20moving%20bases%20where%20machines%20will%20be%20welcomed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20deterrents%20to%20the%20adoption%20of%20AI%20would%20have%20been%20cost.%20The%20big%20US%20corporations%20developing%20the%20technology%20had%20so%20far%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20billions%20of%20dollars%20as%20investment.%20In%20January%2C%20however%2C%20Chinese%20startup%20DeepSeek%20shook%20the%20world%20when%20it%20released%20R1%2C%20a%20model%20that%20has%20a%20radically%20different%20way%20of%20learning%2C%20runs%20on%20relatively%20less%20powerful%20chips%20and%20costs%20a%20tiny%20fraction%20of%20OpenAI's%20or%20Google's%20models.%20It%20surpassed%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20downloads%20on%20the%20Apple%20Store%20within%20a%20week%20of%20release.%20At%20just%20%240.55%20per%20million%20input%20tokens%2C%20the%20R1%20beats%20OpenAI's%20o1%2C%20which%20charges%20%2415%20per%20million%20input%20tokens.%20The%20model%20reportedly%20clocks%20a%2097%25%20success%20rate%20at%20coding%2C%20leaving%20o1%20behind.%20DeepSeek%20could%20trigger%20a%20race%20to%20make%20LLMs%20accessible%20and%20cheap.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Deliberation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarious%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20states%2C%20international%20institutions%20and%20organisations%2C%20business%20coalitions%2C%20and%20civil%20society%20groups%2C%20which%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20design%20governing%20principles%20and%20mechanisms%20for%20the%20development%20and%20deployment%20of%20AI%2C%20are%20congregating%20in%20Paris%20on%20February%2010%20and%2011%20to%20delve%20into%20some%20of%20these%20scenarios.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elysee.fr%2Fen%2Fsommet-pour-l-action-sur-l-ia%5C%22%3EArtificial%20Intelligence%20Action%20Summit%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20somewhat%20of%20an%20emergency%20meeting%2C%20akin%20to%20the%20Earth%20Summit%20in%20Rio%20in%201992%2C%20which%20brought%20the%20environment%20and%20sustainability%20into%20the%20mainstream%20global%20discourse.%20World%20leaders%20and%20those%20helming%20companies%20developing%20futuristic%20technologies%20are%20expected%20to%20deliberate%20on%20evolving%20a%20global%20AI%20framework.%20Future%20of%20Work%20is%20one%20of%20the%20five%20themes%2C%20which%20include%20Public%20Interest%20AI%2C%20Innovation%20and%20Culture%2C%20Trust%20in%20AI%2C%20and%20Global%20AI%20Governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20Europe%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20regulating%20new%20technologies%2C%20it%20will%20likely%20face%20pushback%20from%20the%20new%20administration%20in%20the%20US%20led%20by%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20is%20supported%20by%20some%20of%20the%20leading%20AI%20players.%20Many%20of%20them%20dislike%20the%20European%20regulatory%20approach%E2%80%94central%20to%20which%20is%20individual%20dignity%2C%20personal%20security%20and%20privacy%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20centrality%20of%20freedom%20in%20the%20US%E2%80%94as%20harsh%20and%20anti-innovation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20a%20key%20US%20partner%20in%20technology%20development.%20In%20May%202022%2C%20the%20two%20countries%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2023%2F01%2F31%2Ffact-sheet-united-states-and-india-elevate-strategic-partnership-with-the-initiative-on-critical-and-emerging-technology-icet%2F%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20US-India%20Initiative%20on%20Critical%20and%20Emerging%20Technologies.%20While%20the%20broad%20agreement%20encompasses%20strategic%20technology%20partnership%20and%20defence%20industrial%20cooperation%2C%20it%20has%20a%20specific%20clause%20on%20AI%20that%20is%20vital%20to%20India's%20interests.%20It%20says%20the%20two%20countries%20are%20committed%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdrawing%20from%20global%20efforts%20to%20develop%20common%20standards%20and%20benchmarks%20for%20trustworthy%20AI%20through%20coordinating%20on%20the%20development%20of%20consensus%2C%20multi-stakeholder%20standards%2C%20ensuring%20that%20these%20standards%20and%20benchmarks%20are%20aligned%20with%20democratic%20values%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%2C%20A%20Goldmine%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20broad%20understanding%20on%20aligning%20with%20democratic%20values%20should%20presumably%20include%20protecting%20jobs%20and%20livelihoods%20in%20India.%20After%20all%2C%20India's%20large%2C%20diverse%20population%20makes%20it%20a%20goldmine%20for%20the%20AI%20industry.%20Central%20to%20developing%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20deep%20learning%20is%20tokens%2C%20which%20are%20broken%20down%20fundamental%20bits%20of%20data%2C%20akin%20to%20bytes%20or%20bits%20in%20normal%20computing%20lingo.%20AI%20models%20use%20these%20to%20process%20and%20learn%20from%20data.%20The%20more%20data%20a%20model%20consumes%2C%20the%20better%20and%20faster%20it%20gets.%20Tokens%20transform%20worlds%20into%20knowledge%2C%20turn%20ideas%20into%20videos.%20Tokens%20teach%20robots%20to%20move%20like%20their%20masters%2C%E2%80%9D%20Huang's%20introductory%20presentation%20at%20CES%202025%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20in%20an%20October%202024%20fireside%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dnn3O4GCdHxk%5C%22%3Echat%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20billionaire%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Huang%20said%20that%20Nvidia%20and%20Reliance%20Group%20had%20jointly%20upskilled%20200%2C000%20Indian%20engineers%20to%20work%20on%20AI.%20The%20two%20announced%20that%20they%20plan%20to%20scale%20AI%20infrastructure%20in%20India%20as%20it%20generates%20massive%20amounts%20of%20data%2C%20a%20prerequisite%20for%20creating%20intelligence.%20Ambani%20pointed%20out%20that%20Jio%20had%20delivered%2016%20exabytes%20of%20data%20in%20one%20year%20alone.%20That%20is%20Indians%20hanging%20out%20on%20social%20media%2C%20listening%20to%20audio%20and%20watching%20videos%20on%20streamers%2C%20and%20shopping%20on%20e-commerce%20platforms%20generating%20massive%20amounts%20of%20data.%20Huang%20envisions%20everyone%20in%20India%20using%20AI%2C%20creating%20momentum%20for%20an%20AI%20flywheel.%20Or%20turning%20India%20into%20a%20token%20factory%20for%20future%20Replicants%2C%20the%20economic%20benefits%20of%20which%20will%20flow%20to%20only%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Dinesh%20Narayanan%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20journalist%20and%20author%20of%20'The%20RSS%20And%20The%20Making%20Of%20The%20Deep%20Nation'.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739166360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F821v87ug_replicants_625x300_10_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmove-over-middle-class-replicants-are-coming-7675572%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20envisions%20everyone%20in%20India%20using%20AI%2C%20creating%20momentum%20for%20an%20AI%20flywheel.%20Or%20turning%20India%20into%20a%20token%20factory%20for%20future%20Replicants%2C%20akin%20to%20those%20in%20the%20Harrison%20Ford-starrer%20'Blade%20Runner'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmove-over-middle-class-replicants-are-coming-7675572%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Alaska%20Airlines%20flight%20attendant%20punches%20passenger%20to%20save%20woman%20from%20attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739165989000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118107406%2Cimgsize-4205337.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwatch-alaska-airlines-flight-attendant-punches-passenger-to-save-woman-from-attack%2Farticleshow%2F118103443.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofi