0officer%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20machine%20prepares%20the%20beds%20in%20the%20field%20and%20simultaneously%20plants%20the%20seeds%20on%20the%20bed.%20So%2C%20after%20we%20plough%20the%20field%2C%20we%20let%20the%20machine%20do%20the%20work.%20When%20the%20seeds%20germinate%2C%20we%20supply%20water%20only%20in%20the%20furrows%20of%20the%20beds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20bed%20width%20is%20about%20two%20feet%20and%20the%20furrow%20width%20is%20one%20foot%2C%20water%20is%20supplied%20in%20these%20furrows%20only%20when%20needed.%20This%20method%20ensures%20water%20reaches%20the%20roots%20without%20submerging%20the%20entire%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20this%20technique%20requires%20only%2025%20percent%20of%20the%20water%20traditionally%20used%20for%20paddy%20cultivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETransitioning%20from%20conventional%20methods%20to%20SRB%20was%20not%20without%20its%20challenges.%20The%20technology%20had%20to%20address%20one%20major%20problem%3A%20effective%20weed%20control%20without%20a%20constant%20layer%20of%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20tendency%20for%20weeds%20to%20germinate%20along%20with%20paddy.%20Weeds%20can%20severely%20affect%20paddy%20growth%20by%20competing%20with%20it%20for%20water%20and%20nutrients.%20This%20is%20why%20farmers%20flood%20paddy%20fields%20to%20kill%20weeds.%20To%20overcome%20this%2C%20we%20use%20herbicide-tolerant%20seeds%2C%20which%20have%20been%20given%20to%20us%20by%20the%20Indian%20Agricultural%20Research%20Institute.%20Once%20the%20seeds%20kill%20the%20weeds%2C